name: Y TY – CHASING THE CLOUD IN THE HIGHEST LAND
description: Chasing the cloud in the highest land of  Lao Cai, the North of Viet Nam. Go To Know club promise an unforgettable trip for young people who love nature and being adventurous person. Don’t hesitate to explore the new land and the new things with the marvelous experiences of chasing the clouds, taking your amazing photos and learning some unique traditions of ethnic people. Y Ty would not disappoint your desire of strange and different place.
